  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Kandahar can be booked on either a bed and breakfast or half board, please specify when which you'd prefer at the time of booking.  Please note that half board meals are not available on the 21st Dec and 28th Dec 2024. </p>
<p>Each day a varied continental buffet breakfast with additional hot options is available between 7.30 - 10am.</p>
<p>The half board dinner includes a three course evening meal with a starter, main course with a choice of main (meat or fish) and dessert or cheese. Dinner is served from 7pm.</p>
<p>If you are a vegetarian, we recommend booking bed and breakfast, then eating from the varied <span>à la carte menu (pay locally).  Other dietary requirements cannot be catered for. Please inform us of any dietary requirements at the time of booking.</span></p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
