  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Kandahar is a genuine alpine retreat. The warm atmosphere and Savoyard architecture oozes charm, comfort and well-being. This hotel is located on the vibrant main street of <a data-udi="umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d}" title="Val d'Isere">Val d'Isere, j</a>ust a couple of minutes walk to the slopes. When you have returned from a day on the <a data-udi="umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03}" title="Tignes-Val d’Isere Ski Area">Tignes-Val d'Isere</a> slopes, a cosy lounge bar with a fireplace is the perfect spot to enjoy a drink, or you can soothe any aches and pains in the hotels wellness area. Delicious evening meals are served each day featuring Savoyard classics.</p>
<h2>Alpine style</h2>
<p>The Hotel Kandahar exudes the charm of the Alps with its Savoyard-style décor, which include cosy wood, stone, and soft furnishings. The Hotel Kandahar is a fantastic option for families and groups of friends planning to spend the winter in France, as there are rooms which can accommodate up to four people, each of which features a distinct interior design and gorgeous views of the resort and the mountains in the surrounding area.</p>
<h2>Savoyard specialities</h2>
<p>When you have returned from an active day on the slopes, the Taverne d’Alsace bar and restaurant is the perfect spot to enjoy a cosy night in. Take a seat and enjoy a glass of wine from the varied wine menu or enjoy a traditional aperitif from Alsace. When it comes to dinner a three course evening meal is served each day with traditional regional dishes on offer. You can book a table and order from the extensive a la carte menu if you'd like to treat yourself to an evening meal (pay locally).</p>
<h2>Wellness and relaxation</h2>
<p>After a day of skiing enjoy the benefits of the sauna and hammam, it's a great way to relieve from the aches of skiing or snowboarding. Access to the sauna and steam room is reserved for hotel guests, and is included with your stay.</p>]]></description>
