  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Twin Rooms</strong> are around 20m² and sleep two people. These rooms are also available for sole occupancy with a supplement.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Twin Rooms</strong> are around 25m² and sleep two people.</p>
<p><strong>Family Quad rooms </strong>are around 30m² and sleep up to four people. These rooms have a twin beds or a double bed, and bunk beds in the entrance corridor (suitable for children up to 16 years old). Family rooms are available on request, please give our Reservations team a call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are around 30m² and sleep two people. These rooms have a small seating area. Junior Suites are available on request, please give our Reservations team a call to book.</p>
<p>Interconnecting rooms are available on request. Please note standard rooms will not fit a cot.</p>
<p><strong>Room facilities:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>All rooms have twin or double beds (please specify preference when booking)</li>
<li>Balcony with mountain views</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Satellite TV with English speaking channels</li>
<li>Bathrobes</li>
<li>Towels </li>
<li>Slippers</li>
<li>Hairdryer </li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Phone</li>
<li>Bath with shower head attachment</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
